  "title": "JANITOR SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<ul><li>Work closely with the Manager to ensure smooth operations.</li><li>Supervise & assist a team of crew on site.</li><li>Maintain & control the use of stock, equipment & consumables.</li><li>Assist the Manager in maintaining up-to-date asset list.</li><li>Assist the Manager in scheduling for jobs & holiday leaves.</li><li>Monitor performance & absenteeism of crew.</li><li>Ensure that appropriate PPE are worn by crew.</li><li>Prepare overtime rosters for approval by the Manager.</li><li>Upkeep all equipment.</li><li>Ensure company policies & standards are met by crew at all faclities.</li><li>Liaise & monitor work done by outsourced contractors.</li><li>Other duties assigned by the Manager or the Managerment.</li></ul>",
